cast.overview: Jerry Maguire used to be a typical sports agent: willing to do just about anything he could to get the biggest possible contracts for his clients, plus a nice commission for himself. Then, one day, he suddenly has second thoughts about what he's really doing. When he voices these doubts, he ends up losing his job and all of his clients, save Rod Tidwell, an egomaniacal football player.
cast.title: Jerry Maguire

details.biography: Christine Cavanaugh was an American former voice actress who had a distinctive speaking style and had provided the voice for a large range of cartoon characters. She is best known as the voice of Babe in the hit film, Babe, Chuckie Finster on Rugrats and for being the original voice of Dexter on Dexter's Laboratory. In 2001, she retired from voice acting for personal reasons.
details.name: Christine Cavanaugh
